<tr>
<th style="">Notable ideas</th>
<td class="" style="">Forerunner of <a href="/wiki/Demography" title="Demography">demography</a>, <a href="/wiki/Historiography" title="Historiography">historiography</a>, <a href="/wiki/Cultural_history" title="Cultural history">cultural history</a>, <a href="/wiki/Philosophy_of_history" title="Philosophy of history">philosophy of history</a>, <a href="/wiki/Sociology" title="Sociology">sociology</a>, <a href="/wiki/Social_sciences" title="Social sciences">social sciences</a>, and modern <a href="/wiki/Economics" title="Economics">economics</a>. Developed theories of <a href="/wiki/Asabiyyah" title="Asabiyyah">Asabiyyah</a> and the rise and fall of <a href="/wiki/Civilization" title="Civilization">civilizations</a>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
